data.title: Walbaum Family Tree
data.text: 9 F i Henriette Charlotte Louise Walbaum was born on 16 Mar 1785 in Lenglern, Germany. Henriette married Heinrich Karl Stisser. Heinrich was born on 21 Aug 1773 in Stemmer, Germany. He died on 18 Dec 1844 in Barakamp, Germany. 10 M ii Heinrich Georg Philipp Ludwig Walbaum was born on 29 Mar 1787 in Lenglern, Germany. Heinrich married Dorothea Friederika Johanna Luttgens. 11 M iii Johann Jacob Wilhelm Walbaum was born on 28 Aug 1788 in Lenglern, Germany. He died on 22 Aug 1791 in Lenglern, Germany. 12 F iv Sophie Margarete Walbaum was born on 28 May 1790 in Lenglern, Germany. She died on 18 Jan 1795 in Lenglern, Germany. + 13 M v Friedrich Wilhelm Walbaum 14 M vi Friedrich Conrad Ludwig Walbaum was born on 14 Dec 1793 in Gros Berkel, Germany. He died on 9 Aug 1796 in Gros Berkel, Germany. 15 M vii Karl Hermann Georg Friedrich Walbaum was born on 5 Aug 1795 in Gros Berkel, Germany. Karl married Ulrike Karoline Henriette Luise Lamprecht. Ulrike was born on 2 Jan 1806. She died on 27 Sep 1880 in Burgdorf, Germany. 16 M viii Heinrich Christian Friedrich Walbaum was born on 1 Jun 1797 in Gros Berkel, Germany. Heinrich married Johanne Dorothee Rebentisch. Johanne was born on 19 Jan 1798. She died on 27 Jul 1875. 17 M ix August Gebhard Arnold Walbaum was born on 25 Feb 1798 in Gros Berkel, Germany. He died on 15 Apr 1799 in Gros Berkel, Germany. + 18 M x Heinrich Philipp August Walbaum 19 M xi Wilhelm Albrecht Ernst Walbaum was born on 26 Aug 1801 in Gros Berkel, Germany. He died on 22 Jan 1802 in Gros Berkel, Germany. 20 F xii Antoinette Dorothe Elisabeth Walbaum was born on 1 Apr 1803 in Gros Berkel, Germany. She died on 27 Sep 1804 in Gros Berkel, Germany. 21 M xiii Ludwig Friedrich Arnold Walbaum was born on 10 Jan 1806 in Gros Berkel, Germany. He died on 29 Aug 1865.
